y_of_text','Throughout the heart of the festival program, there is a curated stream of arts and education activity that the Festival coordinates. These arts commissions and digital education awards help bolster the Festivalâ€™s commitment to widening access and engagement with big ideas in contemporary digital culture. '),(1640,259,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(1641,259,'image_5',''),(1642,259,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(1643,259,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(1692,262,'header_image','170'),(1693,262,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(1694,262,'intro_text','We developed a series of advanced HTML5 games for Earth A New Wild, a new series currently airing on American television network PBS. Produced by National Geographic and Passion Planet, the series takes a fresh look at humankindâ€™s relationship to the planetâ€™s wildest places and most fascinating species.'),(1695,262,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(1696,262,'image_1','238'),(1697,262,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(1698,262,'image_2','239'),(1699,262,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(1700,262,'image_3','240'),(1701,262,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(1702,262,'image_4','241'),(1703,262,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(1704,262,'main_body_of_text','Tilt have created a new microsite which is inspired by content from the series. The Ecosystem Explorer is a collection of videos, games, and infographics designed to take students deep into the ecosystems of three thrilling animals: vultures, wolves, and sharks.\r\n\r\nRelated videos introduce each ecosystem and explore the relationship between animals and humans which is often more complicated than we realize. The microsite has been developed to encourage students to discover more about the ecology and conservation of these three worlds by exploring games, videos and infographics.\r\n\r\nBuilt using Create JS, Tilt showcased their advanced knowledge of HTML5 to take the project beyond the Flash requirements of the brief to an exciting new level. Tilt also developed dynamic illustrations for the games which were enhanced by suitably graphic sound effects!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pbslearningmedia.org/resource/5aeed659-7f0b-417f-81d9-5f2e9c747644/ecosystem-explorer-earth-a-new-wild/\" target=\"_blank\">Experience it for yourself.</a>'),(1705,262,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(1706,262,'image_5','247'),(1707,262,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(1708,262,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(1711,263,'header_image','175'),(1712,263,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(1713,263,'intro_text','Throughout the course of the year select members of the Tilt team have been battling the elements in an attempt to build up the stamina required to face the â€˜Tough Mudderâ€™ challenge. '),(1714,263,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(1715,263,'image_1','224'),(1716,263,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(1717,263,'image_2','225'),(1718,263,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(1719,263,'image_3','226'),(1720,263,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(1721,263,'image_4','227'),(1722,263,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(1723,263,'main_body_of_text','Tough Mudder is a team-oriented 10-12 mile (18-20 km) obstacle course designed to test physical strength and mental grit. Putting Camaraderie over finisher rankings this event allows participants to experience world class obstacles. Well this is what the events site said, but to be perfectly honest with you, we all just fancied the chance to get really really muddy! Whats not to like? Check out our <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/130366057\" target=\"_blank\">training video</a> . . . if you can call it training!\r\n\r\nThe course took a little over 3 hours, with some great new obstacles introduced by the Tough Mudder team. Our favorites were <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/obstacles/king-swingers\" target=\"_blank\">King of the Swingers</a> and  <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/content/mud-mile-20\" target=\"_blank\">Mud Mile</a>, with the latter seei