 hoping to have him join their project discussions. \r\n\r\nTop marks Elliot.\r\n'),(4288,460,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(4289,460,'single_image',''),(4290,460,'_single_image','field_5629ea2db47b2'),(4291,460,'header_image','459'),(4292,460,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(4293,460,'standfirst_text','A hotly debated topic, a quick note on the importance of a positive internship programme and a great intern working within it.'),(4294,460,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(4295,460,'vimeo_id',''),(4296,460,'_vimeo_id','field_5629e91cf9252'),(4297,460,'youtube_id',''),(4298,460,'_youtube_id','field_5629e94ef9253'),(4299,460,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(4300,461,'image_1',''),(4301,461,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(4302,461,'image_2',''),(4303,461,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(4304,461,'image_3',''),(4305,461,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(4306,461,'image_4',''),(4307,461,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(4308,461,'main_content_area','Internships are often a touchy topic for a lot of businesses within a lot of industries. Without much information or context, they are often assumed to be the first-word equivalent of free-labour or ‘the thing you do to pay your dues to the industry’. Whilst you’ll probably agree or disagree on this notion, there is no debate that some organisations create and accept internships often with a desperate, even negative agenda. It’s the drab fact of the workplace and over the years has been called out by various governments and institutions. Though change has occurred over time, it’s worth noting, when I was but a poor and simple student, the idea of working religiously for a company who wanted to pay me the financial equivalent of a dairylea lunchable, had me somewhat hesitant. \r\n\r\nLuckily at the madhouse that is Tilt, things are very different, and have been different way before I joined. Long-term internships are hugely beneficial and a great deal of the team started off as one. I believe th