ng up with tasks and challenges that would have the very best of us sometimes at a bit of a loss. Direct quote: \'I don\'t know if this is even possible, so ideally like to see two options...\', I can only apologise to him for my deliberate ambiguity/challenging approach. It\'s been entirely for my benefit as a means of scouting his skills. And so far he has been showing it in abundance. Following his dedication and work-rate, he now finds himself frequently approached by more and more staff members hoping to have him join their project discussions. \r\n\r\nTop marks Elliot.\r\n'),(4390,468,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(4391,468,'single_image',''),(4392,468,'_single_image','field_5629ea2db47b2'),(4393,468,'header_image','457'),(4394,468,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(4395,468,'standfirst_text','A quick note on the importance of a positive internship programme and a great intern working within it.'),(4396,468,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(4397,468,'vimeo_id',''),(4398,468,'_vimeo_id','field_5629e91cf9252'),(4399,468,'youtube_id',''),(4400,468,'_youtube_id','field_5629e94ef9253'),(4401,468,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(4404,469,'image_1','463'),(4405,469,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(4406,469,'image_2','464'),(4407,469,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(4408,469,'image_3','465'),(4409,469,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(4410,469,'image_4','466'),(4411,469,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(4412,469,'main_content_area','Internships are often a touchy topic for a lot of businesses within a lot of industries. Without much information or context, they are often assumed to be the first-word equivalent of free-labour or ‘the thing you do to pay your dues to the industry’. Whilst you’ll probably agree or disagree on this notion, there is no debate that some organisations create and accept internships often with a desperate, even negative agenda. It’s the drab fact of the workplace and over the years has been called out by various go