ond what they are learning in school.\r\n\r\nFeaturing some of Nickelodeons most popular characters, including Spongebob and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, the Code-It experience extends beyond straight education and encourages kids to explore the application and develop their skills with awards, challenges and a bustling community to get involved in.\r\n\r\nFor more information about this project visit our <a href=\"../code-it\">work page</a>, or alternatively <a href=\"http://www.nick.co.uk/_/code-it/\" target=\"_blank\">have a go yourself</a>. '),(5401,533,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(5402,102,'vimeo_id_two',''),(5403,102,'_vimeo_id_two','field_564b0ac8ebbf4'),(5406,534,'header_image','391'),(5407,534,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(5408,534,'standfirst_text','Run by the Brighton Chamber of Commerce, the Summit is a fantastic event that attracts local and national businesses alike; for a day geared around growing their business. We had the pleasure of both filming and speaking at the event this year. '),(5409,534,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(5410,534,'image_1',''),(5411,534,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(5412,534,'image_2',''),(5413,534,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(5414,534,'image_3',''),(5415,534,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(5416,534,'image_4',''),(5417,534,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(5418,534,'single_image',''),(5419,534,'_single_image','field_5629ea2db47b2'),(5420,534,'vimeo_id',''),(5421,534,'_vimeo_id','field_5629e91cf9252'),(5422,534,'vimeo_id_two',''),(5423,534,'_vimeo_id_two','field_564b0ac8ebbf4'),(5424,534,'youtube_id','C8OqQ2Kowbk'),(5425,534,'_youtube_id','field_5629e94ef9253'),(5426,534,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(5427,534,'main_content_area',''),(5428,534,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(5431,535,'header_image','391'),(5432,535,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(5433,535,'standfirst_text','Run by the Brighton Chamber of Commerce, the Summit is a fantastic event that attract