 neighbourhood that is now the heart of Brighton\'s blooming digital community. The huge interior – the largest nave in England - offered an amazing opportunity in which to grow a digital lightening storm, released from the hands of a child.\r\n\r\nThe film is shot in 6k RED cinema to obtain film industry standard image quality at high frame rates (for slow motion). We played with FumeFX and Elementacular for Maya to produce realistic evolving 3d rain clouds, used Optical Flares in AfterEffects to give it an epic anamorphic look, and graded the footage with DaVinci Resolve.'),(6793,631,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(6794,639,'header_image','633'),(6795,639,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(6796,639,'standfirst_text','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.'),(6797,639,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(6798,639,'image_1','634'),(6799,639,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(6800,639,'image_2','635'),(6801,639,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(6802,639,'image_3','636'),(6803,639,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(6804,639,'image_4','637'),(6805,639,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(6806,639,'single_image',''),(6807,639,'_single_image','field_5629ea2db47b2'),(6808,639,'vimeo_id','138625045'),(6809,639,'_vimeo_id','field_5629e91cf9252'),(6810,639,'vimeo_id_two',''),(6811,639,'_vimeo_id_two','field_564b0ac8ebbf4'),(6812,639,'youtube_id',''),(6813,639,'_youtube_id','field_5629e94ef9253'),(6814,639,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(6815,639,'main_content_area','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit 