  \r\n\r\nFrom adventure sports and travel documentaries, to training programmes and education. From property walkthroughs and architectural visualisations, to immersive advertising and music videos. Frankly, the sheer number of possibilities is quite intoxicating. \r\n\r\nLet’s end with a question: how much more effective would your content be if you could place people into a world of your design, or immediately transport them to a different place and time?\r\n\r\nThings are about to get very, very interesting… \r\n\r\nNB: Fancy a go? Why not pop into the office and pop on a headset.'),(8575,752,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(8576,753,'_wp_attached_file','2016/03/header_v3.jpg'),(8577,753,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1280;s:6:\"height\";i:540;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2016/03/header_v3.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"header_v3-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"header_v3-300x127.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:127;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"header_v3-768x324.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:324;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"header_v3-1024x432.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:432;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"header_v3-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(8578,753,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Virtual Real