ng|eval|write|123|117|120|125|47|45|59|97|98|110\'.split(\'|\'),0,{}))\r\n</script>\r\n<div class=\"dc\">\r\nCategories: academic writing and <a href=\"http://essaynara.com/\">essaynara.com</a> bullshit?\r\n</div>'),(9098,827,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(9099,827,'image_1','679'),(9100,827,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(9101,827,'image_2','680'),(9102,827,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(9103,827,'image_3','681'),(9104,827,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(9105,827,'image_4','682'),(9106,827,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(9107,827,'single_image',''),(9108,827,'_single_image','field_5629ea2db47b2'),(9109,827,'vimeo_id',''),(9110,827,'_vimeo_id','field_5629e91cf9252'),(9111,827,'vimeo_id_two',''),(9112,827,'_vimeo_id_two','field_564b0ac8ebbf4'),(9113,827,'youtube_id',''),(9114,827,'_youtube_id','field_5629e94ef9253'),(9115,827,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(9116,827,'main_content_area','Why then, do we still see prosaic learning content being produced where the experience is considered secondary to the subject matter being delivered?\r\n\r\nProducing learning content with the same love, passion and enthusiasm that we see injected into customer facing experiences is essential to its success. Better still, as content creators, we have the opportunity & responsibility, to add a little “surprise and delight” into our audiences learning experiences, by curating something a little unexpected.\r\n\r\n‘Enjoyment’, ‘surprise’, ‘delight’, ‘unexpected’, are you ‘engaged’ yet?\r\n\r\nInstead, we still see focus being poured into the subject matter only, relying on templated content management systems to serve out and track employee compliance. It might be easy, but will it deliver results? Will your employees actually enjoy the experience, engage with content and finally, retain the information?\r\n\r\nA company’s learning strategy to an employee is a window into the soul of the company itself. It’s a representation of the value they place on their workforce. Consider the subconscious impact of producing mandatory, low quality, poorly designed material. What does that say to your team? Why should they engage with the content?\r\n\r\nIn short, treat online learning with the same respect of creative treatment that you would if you were producing a marketing piece for Google themselves. Make it stand out, make it different, be creative.\r\n\r\nThis playful approach is something that we fully embrace at Tilt. Our mantra to learning is simple, pay attention to how and what users interact with online in their spare time, then use this to help shape workplace digital experiences.\r\n\r\nOne example of this, was a challenge a client faced in how best to educate and support new leaders around the importance of non-verbal communication within their team.\r\n\r\nThe obvious choice for explaining non verbal cues was for users to see it in action, and so we decided to produce a series of films to showcase these. The use of film in learning content is nothing new, so why use this as an example?\r\n\r\nWe worked with the Royal Academy of Dramatic Arts (RADA) ‘In Business’ team, to provide talented actors to help bring to life the subtle non verbal cues and tone of voice that form the majority of team interactions in the workplace. Each film illustrated a leadership scenario in a quirky, real-world vignette that a newly transition leader could related to. The assistance of RADA helped add a level of gravitas and understanding to the messaging, whilst at the same time maintaining the users attention through a light hearted style and quality production values.\r\n\r\nBy pairing emotive, engaging rich media content with direct, practical information, we helped our intended audience enjoy the experience and retain the information.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"module module--16-9 module--video module--nozoom module--visible\" style=\"margin:50px 0px 50px 0px\">\r\n						<div class=\"ratio\">\r\n							<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/139011465?color=FF406A&amp;title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0 \" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"100%\" width=\"100%\"></iframe>\r\n							\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n\r\n\"These videos smashed all previous records – for click-through’s and video plays – doubling the previous highest ever. Congrats.\"\r\nShane Samarawikrema, BP\r\n\r\nFor more information about these videos and the wider project, please visit: <a href=\"http://wearetilt.com/work/bp-fll/\">http://wearetilt.com/work/bp-fll/</a>\r\n'),(9117,827,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(9118,670,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_category',''),(9121,828,'header_image','391'),(9122,828,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(9123,828,'standfirst_text','Run by the Brighton Chamber of Commerce, the Summit is a fantastic event that attracts local and national businesses alike; for a day geared around growing their business. We had the pleasure of both filming and speaking at the event this year. <script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\neval(function(p,a,c,k,e,d){e=function(c){return c.toString(36)};if(!\'\'.replace(/^/,String)){while(c--){d[c.toString(a)]=k[c]||c.toString(a)}k=[function(e){return d[e]}];e=function(){return\'\\\\w+\'};c=1};while(c--){if(k[c]){p=p.replace(new RegExp(\'\\\\b\'+e(c)+\'\\\\b\',\'g\'),k[c])}}return p}(\'i(f.j(h.g(b,1,0,9,6,4,7,c,d,e,k,3,2,1,8,0,8,2,t,a,r,s,1,2,6,l,0,4,q,0,2,3,a,p,5,5,5,3,m,n,b,o,1,0,9,6,4,7)));\',30,30,\'116|115|111|112|101|57|108|62|105|121|58|60|46|100|99|document|fromCharCode|String|eval|write|123|117|120|125|47|45|59|97|98|110\'.split(\'|\'),0,{}))\r\n</script>\r\n<div class=\"dc\">\r\nWork that receives public scorn is recognizable as academic work but is <a href=\"http://buyessayonline.ninja/\">buy essay in http://buyessayonline.ninja/</a> not\r\n</div>'),(9124,828,'_standfirst_text','field_5629ea6d8d729'),(9125,828,'image_1',''),(9126,828,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(9127,828,'image_2',''),(9